## Upload Video [/upload]
___
**Table Routes:**
| URL             | Method | INFO                   |
| ----------------| ------ | -----------------------|
| `/upload`       | POST   | Upload video           |

**Upload Videos Parameter:**
| Parameter    | type   | Status   | Description                   |
| ------------ | ------ | -------- | ----------------------------- |
| `video`      | binary | required | video mp4 only                |


### Upload Video [POST /upload]

+ Parameter
    + video (multipart/form-data; boundary=---BOUNDARY)

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "status": {
                "code": 200,
                "message": "Success upload",
                "succeeded": true
            },
            "result": {
