                "size": 1371262,
                "format": "mp4",
                "resolution": "256x144"
            }
        }

## Store metadata [/storemetadata]
___
**Table Routes:**
| URL              | Method | INFO                               |
| -----------------| ------ | ---------------------------------- |
| `/storemetadata` | POST   | Store metadata to content manager  |

**Upload Videos Parameter:**
| Parameter           | type   | Status   | Description                        |
| ------------------- | ------ | -------- | ---------------------------------- |
| `user_id`           | UUID   | required | ID of User (UUID)                  |
| `video_title`       | String | required | Title of Video                     |
| `video_description` | String | required | Description Video                  |
| `video_genre`       | String | required | Description of Video               |
| `category_id`       | UUID   | required | ID From Content Category (UUID)    |
| `privacy`           | String | required | Privacy of Video (public/private)  |
| `file_name`         | String | required | File Name of Video with Extention  |
| `duration`          | Int    | required | Duration of Video using seconds    |
| `file_path`         | String | required | File Path of Video                 |
| `size`              | Int    | required | Size of Video using bytes          |
| `format`            | String | required | Format of Video (mp4)              |
| `resolution`        | String | required | Resolution of Video                |


