## Save Video [/savevideo/{userid}/{id_content_metadata}]
___
**Table Routes:**
| URL                                        | Method | INFO           |
| ------------------------------------------ | ------ | ---------------|
| `savevideo/{userid}/{id_content_metadata}` | GET    | Save Video     |


### Save Video [GET /savevideo/{userid}/{id_content_metadata}]

+ Parameter
    + userid: `05237edb-4f5d-432d-9321-42a352804c29` (string, required) - Id of User
    + id_content_metadata: `104784f7-8df2-4b1d-9de6-53307eeff3b8` (string, required) - Id of Content Metadata

+ Response 200 (application/json)

        {
            "status": {
                "code": 200,
                "message": "data has been saved"
            },
            "result": {
                "id_user": "05237edb-4f5d-432d-9321-42a352804c29",
                "id_content_metadata": "104784f7-8df2-4b1d-9de6-53307eeff3b8"
            }
        }
        
## Download Video [/downloadvideo/{id_content_metadata}/{filename}]
___
**Table Routes:**
| URL                                              | Method | INFO            |
| ------------------------------------------------ | ------ | --------------- |
| `downloadvideo/{id_content_metadata}/{filename}` | GET    | Download Video  |


### Download Video [GET /downloadvideo/{id_content_metadata}/{filename}]

+ Parameter
    + id_content_metadata: `104784f7-8df2-4b1d-9de6-53307eeff3b8` (string, required) - Id of Content Metadata
    + filename: `e60019ea-09e5-4727-9f26-262d118e8ad3` (string, required) - filename without extention

+ Response 200 (video/mp4)